explanation_en: Setting AMF IP address to the same value as gNB's NG-AMF interface will cause IP routing conflicts, making AMF unreachable and leading to NG setup failures.

explanation_zh: 將 gNB NG-AMF 位址設定為無效 IP (八位元組 > 255) 會導致網路介面綁定失敗和 NG-AMF 通訊中斷。

explanation_zh: 將 gNB 用於 NG-AMF 介面的 IP 位址設定為與 AMF 相同的位址會導致 IP 位址衝突，阻止網路通訊並造成 NG 介面建立失敗。

explanation_en: Setting AMF IP address to an unreachable subnet will cause routing failure, preventing NG interface establishment and AMF communication.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 位址設定為不可達的子網路會導致路由失敗，阻止 NG 介面建立和 AMF 通訊。

explanation_en: Setting NGu IP address to an unreachable subnet will cause routing failure for user plane traffic, preventing UPF communication and data transmission.
explanation_zh: 將 NGu IP 位址設定為不可達的子網路會導致使用者平面流量的路由失敗，阻止 UPF 通訊和資料傳輸。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP address to an external subnet IP will cause interface binding failure on the loopback interface, preventing F1 connection establishment.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 位址設定為外部子網路 IP 會導致在回環介面上的介面綁定失敗，阻止 F1 連線建立。

explanation_en: Setting remote SCTP address to an external subnet IP will cause connection failure to the DU, preventing F1 interface establishment.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 位址設定為外部子網路 IP 會導致與 DU 的連線失敗，阻止 F1 介面建立。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP interface name to a non-existent interface will cause binding failure, preventing F1 connection establishment.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 介面名稱設定為不存在的介面會導致綁定失敗，阻止 F1 連線建立。

explanation_en: Setting transport preference to an unknown enum value will cause interface selection failure, preventing proper communication setup.
explanation_zh: 將傳輸偏好設定為未知的枚舉值會導致介面選擇失敗，阻止正確的通訊設定。

explanation_en: Setting NR cell ID to 0, which is reserved, will cause cell identification failure and registration issues.
explanation_zh: 將 NR 小區 ID 設定為 0（保留值）會導致小區識別失敗並造成註冊問題。

explanation_en: Changing gNB_ID to number instead of hex string will cause parsing error in ID processing.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 改為數字而非十六進位字串會在 ID 處理中造成解析錯誤。

explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to 0, which is reserved, will cause TAC validation failure and cell registration issues.
explanation_zh: 將 tracking_area_code 設定為 0（保留值）會導致 TAC 驗證失敗並造成小區註冊問題。

explanation_en: Port 0 is invalid for network communication, causing connection failure.
explanation_zh: 連接埠 0 對於網路通訊無效，導致連線失敗。

explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP control port to a value above the valid range (0-65535) will cause socket connection failure, preventing F1 interface establishment.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 控制埠設定為超出有效範圍 (0-65535) 的值，會導致套接字連線失敗，阻止 F1 介面建立。

explanation_en: Changing the remote SCTP data port to string instead of number will cause parsing error during configuration loading, preventing F1 data plane establishment.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 資料埠改為字串而非數字，會在配置載入期間導致解析錯誤，阻止 F1 資料平面建立。

explanation_en: Zero streams will cause SCTP association failure.
explanation_zh: 零個串流會導致 SCTP 關聯失敗。

explanation_en: Invalid IP address will cause socket binding failure.
explanation_zh: 無效的 IP 位址會導致 socket 綁定失敗。

explanation_en: An invalid IP address format for the remote SCTP address will cause connection failure to the DU, preventing F1 interface establishment.
explanation_zh: 遠端 SCTP 位址的無效 IP 格式會導致與 DU 的連線失敗，阻止 F1 介面建立。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP interface name to null will cause interface binding failure, preventing F1 connection establishment.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 介面名稱設定為 null 會導致介面綁定失敗，阻止 F1 連線建立。

explanation_en: Setting local_s_portc to the same value as remote_s_portc will cause port conflict in SCTP connection, leading to connection failure.
explanation_zh: 將 local_s_portc 設定為與 remote_s_portc 相同的值會在 SCTP 連線中造成連接埠衝突，導致連線失敗。

explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to a negative value will cause the system to fail during thread initialization, leading to gNB startup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 Num_Threads_PUSCH 設定為負值會在執行緒初始化期間導致系統失敗，造成 gNB 啟動失敗。

explanation_en: Changing Asn1_verbosity to a number instead of string will cause parsing error in the configuration loader, preventing the config from being loaded.
explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 改為數字而非字串會在配置載入器中造成解析錯誤，阻止配置被載入。

explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to a different subnet makes it unreachable, causing NG-AP connection failure and preventing gNB registration.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 位址設定為不同子網路會使其無法連線，導致 NG-AP 連線失敗並阻止 gNB 註冊。

explanation_en: Setting the CU's NG AMF interface IP to a different subnet makes the AMF unreachable, causing NG interface binding failure and registration rejection.
explanation_zh: 將 CU 的 NG AMF 介面 IP 設定為不同子網路會使 AMF 無法連線，導致 NG 介面綁定失敗並造成註冊被拒絕。

explanation_en: Setting the CU's NGU interface IP to a different subnet makes the UPF unreachable, causing NG-U interface failure and data path disruption.
explanation_zh: 將 CU 的 NGU 介面 IP 設定為不同子網路會使 UPF 無法連線，導致 NG-U 介面失敗並造成資料路徑中斷。

explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to a different subnet makes the DU unreachable, causing F1 interface connection failure and cell setup rejection.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 位址設定為不同子網路會使 DU 無法連線，導致 F1 介面連線失敗並造成小區設定被拒絕。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP address the same as the remote address causes IP address conflict, leading to SCTP socket binding failure and F1 interface setup error.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 位址設定為與遠端位址相同會造成 IP 位址衝突，導致 SCTP socket 綁定失敗並造成 F1 介面設定錯誤。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP control port to a value outside the valid range (0-65535) causes socket creation failure, leading to SCTP connection establishment error and F1 interface failure.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為超出有效範圍 (0-65535) 的值會造成 socket 建立失敗，導致 SCTP 連線建立錯誤並造成 F1 介面失敗。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP control port the same as the remote port causes port conflict during SCTP association setup, leading to connection failure and F1 interface rejection.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為與遠端連接埠相同會在 SCTP 關聯設定期間造成連接埠衝突，導致連線失敗並造成 F1 介面被拒絕。

explanation_en: Setting SCTP instreams to 0 violates the minimum requirement for SCTP streams, causing SCTP association establishment failure and F1 interface connection error.
explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸入流設定為 0 違反了 SCTP 流的 minimum 要求，導致 SCTP 關聯建立失敗並造成 F1 介面連線錯誤。

explanation_en: Changing SCTP instreams to a string instead of an integer causes type validation error during configuration parsing, preventing the config from being loaded.
explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸入流改為字串而非整數會在配置解析期間造成類型驗證錯誤，阻止配置被載入。

explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to an unknown enum value will cause security negotiation failure during the initial security setup phase, leading to NAS registration rejection.
explanation_zh: 將加密算法設定為未知的枚舉值會在初始安全設定階段導致安全協商失敗，造成 NAS 註冊被拒絕。

explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.
explanation_zh: 將完整性算法設定為未知的枚舉值 'nia9'，會在安全協商階段導致協商失敗，並造成 NAS 註冊被拒絕。

explanation_en: Changing drb_ciphering to a number instead of a string causes type validation error during configuration parsing, preventing the config from being loaded.
explanation_zh: 將 drb_ciphering 改為數字而非字串會在配置解析期間造成類型驗證錯誤，阻止配置被載入。

explanation_en: Using an invalid log level will cause the logging system to fail initialization, resulting in no logs being produced and potential debugging issues.
explanation_zh: 使用無效的日誌級別會導致日誌系統初始化失敗，造成沒有日誌產生並可能出現除錯問題。

explanation_en: An invalid gNB ID format will cause configuration validation failure, preventing the gNB from starting up properly.
explanation_zh: 無效的 gNB ID 格式會導致配置驗證失敗，阻止 gNB 正確啟動。

explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a negative value violates the valid range for cell IDs, causing cell setup failure and preventing UE attachment.
explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為負值違反了小區 ID 的有效範圍，導致小區設定失敗並阻止 UE 附接。

explanation_en: Setting mcc to a value outside the valid range (000-999) causes PLMN validation failure, preventing network registration and UE connectivity.
explanation_zh: 將 mcc 設定為超出有效範圍 (000-999) 的值會導致 PLMN 驗證失敗，阻止網路註冊和 UE 連線。

explanation_en: Setting mnc to a value outside the valid range (00-999) causes PLMN validation failure, preventing network registration and UE connectivity.
explanation_zh: 將 mnc 設定為超出有效範圍 (00-999) 的值會導致 PLMN 驗證失敗，阻止網路註冊和 UE 連線。

explanation_en: Setting mnc_length to a value outside the valid range (2-3) causes PLMN validation failure, preventing network registration and UE connectivity.
explanation_zh: 將 mnc_length 設定為超出有效範圍 (2-3) 的值會導致 PLMN 驗證失敗，阻止網路註冊和 UE 連線。

explanation_en: Setting sst to a value outside the valid range (0-255) causes NSSAI validation failure, preventing network slice selection and UE connectivity.
explanation_zh: 將 sst 設定為超出有效範圍 (0-255) 的值會導致 NSSAI 驗證失敗，阻止網路切片選擇和 UE 連線。

explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to a negative value violates the valid range for TAC, causing UE attachment failure and preventing connectivity.
explanation_zh: 將 tracking_area_code 設定為負值違反了 TAC 的有效範圍，導致 UE 附接失敗並阻止連線。

explanation_en: Setting tr_s_preference to an unknown enum value causes transport preference validation failure, preventing F1 interface setup and cell activation.
explanation_zh: 將 tr_s_preference 設定為未知的枚舉值會導致傳輸偏好驗證失敗，阻止 F1 介面設定和小區啟動。

explanation_en: Changing local_s_if_name to a number instead of a string causes interface name validation error, preventing SCTP socket binding and F1 connection establishment.
explanation_zh: 將 local_s_if_name 改為數字而非字串會造成介面名稱驗證錯誤，阻止 SCTP socket 綁定和 F1 連線建立。

explanation_en: Changing gNB_name to a number instead of a string causes name validation error, preventing proper gNB identification and configuration loading.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB_name 改為數字而非字串會造成名稱驗證錯誤，阻止正確的 gNB 識別和配置載入。

explanation_en: Changing Active_gNBs to a string instead of an array causes list validation error, preventing gNB activation and system startup.
explanation_zh: 將 Active_gNBs 改為字串而非陣列會造成列表驗證錯誤，阻止 gNB 啟動和系統啟動。

explanation_en: Changing ciphering_algorithms to a string instead of an array causes list validation error, preventing security algorithm configuration and UE authentication.
explanation_zh: 將 ciphering_algorithms 改為字串而非陣列會造成列表驗證錯誤，阻止安全算法配置和 UE 認證。

explanation_en: Changing integrity_algorithms to a string instead of an array causes list validation error, preventing security algorithm configuration and UE authentication.
explanation_zh: 將 integrity_algorithms 改為字串而非陣列會造成列表驗證錯誤，阻止安全算法配置和 UE 認證。

explanation_en: Setting the NG AMF IP address to loopback causes routing failure, as the AMF is not reachable via 127.0.0.1, leading to NG interface connection failure.
explanation_zh: 將 NG AMF IP 位址設定為回環位址會導致路由失敗，因為 AMF 無法透過 127.0.0.1 連線，造成 NG 介面連線失敗。

explanation_zh: 將遠端 S 位址設定為不同私有網路 IP 會使 DU 無法連線，造成 F1 介面連線失敗。

explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為 0 無效，會造成 NG 設定中的身份衝突。

explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to 0 is invalid, causing cell identity conflict.
explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為 0 無效，會造成細胞身份衝突。

explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to 0 is invalid, causing TAU failure.
explanation_zh: 將 tracking_area_code 設定為 0 無效，會造成 TAU 失敗。

explanation_en: Setting mcc to 0 is invalid, causing PLMN mismatch and registration failure.
explanation_zh: 將 mcc 設定為 0 無效，會造成 PLMN 不匹配並導致註冊失敗。

explanation_en: Setting mnc to 0 is invalid, causing PLMN mismatch and registration failure.
explanation_zh: 將 mnc 設定為 0 無效，會造成 PLMN 不匹配並導致註冊失敗。

explanation_en: Setting sst to 0 is invalid, causing slice mismatch and registration failure.
explanation_zh: 將 sst 設定為 0 無效，會造成切片不匹配並導致註冊失敗。

explanation_en: Setting mnc_length to 0 is invalid, causing PLMN parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 mnc_length 設定為 0 無效，會造成 PLMN 解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting tr_s_preference to invalid enum will cause transport preference parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 tr_s_preference 設定為無效枚舉會造成傳輸偏好解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting local_s_if_name to number instead of string will cause interface binding failure.
explanation_zh: 將 local_s_if_name 設定為數字而非字串會造成介面綁定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to number instead of string will cause configuration parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB_name 設定為數字而非字串會造成配置解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to invalid enum will cause ASN.1 verbosity parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為無效枚舉會造成 ASN.1 詳細程度解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting Active_gNBs to string instead of array will cause active gNB parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 Active_gNBs 設定為字串而非陣列會造成活躍 gNB 解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting drb_ciphering to invalid enum will cause security configuration parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 drb_ciphering 設定為無效枚舉會造成安全配置解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting drb_integrity to invalid enum will cause security configuration parsing failure.
explanation_zh: 將 drb_integrity 設定為無效枚舉會造成安全配置解析失敗。

explanation_en: Setting ciphering algorithm to invalid enum will cause security negotiation failure and NAS registration rejection.
explanation_zh: 將加密算法設定為無效枚舉會造成安全協商失敗並導致 NAS 註冊被拒絕。

explanation_en: Setting integrity algorithm to invalid enum will cause security negotiation failure and NAS registration rejection.
explanation_zh: 將完整性算法設定為無效枚舉會造成安全協商失敗並導致 NAS 註冊被拒絕。

explanation_en: Setting AMF IP to an invalid address with octet 256 will cause the CU to fail connecting to AMF, leading to NG interface setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 設定為無效位址（八位元組 256）會導致 CU 無法連接到 AMF，造成 NG 介面設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting GNB IP for NG AMF to an invalid address with octet 256 will cause the CU to fail binding to the interface, leading to NG setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 NG AMF 的 GNB IP 設定為無效位址（八位元組 256）會導致 CU 無法綁定介面，造成 NG 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting GNB IP for NGU to an invalid address with octet 256 will cause the CU to fail binding to the UPF interface, leading to NG-U setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 NGU 的 GNB IP 設定為無效位址（八位元組 256）會導致 CU 無法綁定 UPF 介面，造成 NG-U 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP address to an invalid IP with octet 256 will cause the CU to fail binding to the F1 interface, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 位址設定為無效 IP（八位元組 256）會導致 CU 無法綁定 F1 介面，造成 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting remote SCTP address to an invalid IP with octet 256 will cause the CU to fail connecting to the DU, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 位址設定為無效 IP（八位元組 256）會導致 CU 無法連接到 DU，造成 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting SCTP INSTREAMS to a negative value will cause SCTP initialization failure, leading to F1 connection failure.
explanation_zh: 將 SCTP INSTREAMS 設定為負值會導致 SCTP 初始化失敗，造成 F1 連線失敗。

explanation_en: Setting SCTP OUTSTREAMS to a negative value will cause SCTP initialization failure, leading to F1 connection failure.
explanation_zh: 將 SCTP OUTSTREAMS 設定為負值會導致 SCTP 初始化失敗，造成 F1 連線失敗。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP control port to 0 will cause socket binding failure, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為 0 會導致 socket 綁定失敗，造成 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting remote SCTP control port to 0 will cause connection failure to DU, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為 0 會導致無法連接到 DU，造成 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP data port to 0 will cause socket binding failure, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 資料連接埠設定為 0 會導致 socket 綁定失敗，造成 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting remote SCTP data port to 0 will cause connection failure to DU, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 資料連接埠設定為 0 會導致無法連接到 DU，造成 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting GNB port for S1U to 0 will cause socket binding failure, leading to NG-U setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 GNB S1U 連接埠設定為 0 會導致 socket 綁定失敗，造成 NG-U 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP control port to the same value as remote SCTP control port will cause port conflict in SCTP connection, leading to F1 setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為與遠端 SCTP 控制連接埠相同的值會在 SCTP 連線中造成連接埠衝突，導致 F1 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting AMF IP to the same as CU's NG AMF IP will cause the CU to try connecting to itself, leading to NG setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 設定為與 CU NG AMF IP 相同會導致 CU 嘗試連接到自己，造成 NG 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting GNB IP for NGU to the AMF IP will cause routing confusion, leading to NG-U setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 NGU 的 GNB IP 設定為 AMF IP 會導致路由混亂，造成 NG-U 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting local SCTP address to the same as GNB NG AMF IP will cause IP address conflict, leading to F1 interface failure.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 位址設定為與 GNB NG AMF IP 相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 F1 介面失敗。

explanation_en: Setting remote SCTP address to the same as GNB NG AMF IP will cause IP address conflict, leading to F1 connection failure.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 位址設定為與 GNB NG AMF IP 相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 F1 連線失敗。

explanation_en: Setting AMF IP to the same as local SCTP address will cause IP address conflict, leading to NG setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 設定為與本地 SCTP 位址相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 NG 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting GNB IP for NG AMF to the same as local SCTP address will cause IP address conflict, leading to NG setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 NG AMF 的 GNB IP 設定為與本地 SCTP 位址相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 NG 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting GNB IP for NGU to the same as local SCTP address will cause IP address conflict, leading to NG-U setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 NGU 的 GNB IP 設定為與本地 SCTP 位址相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 NG-U 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting AMF IP to the same as remote SCTP address will cause IP address conflict, leading to NG setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 設定為與遠端 SCTP 位址相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 NG 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting the gNB's NG-AMF IP address to the same as the AMF IP will cause IP address conflict, leading to NG interface setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB 的 NG-AMF IP 位址設定為與 AMF IP 相同會導致 IP 位址衝突，造成 NG 介面設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to a different private network range without proper routing configuration will cause the gNB to be unable to establish connection with the AMF, leading to NG interface setup failure and gNB registration failure.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 位址設定為不同的私有網路範圍而沒有適當的路由配置，會導致 gNB 無法與 AMF 建立連線，造成 NG 介面設定失敗和 gNB 註冊失敗。

explanation_en: Setting the gNB's NG-AMF interface IP to a different private network range without routing will make the AMF unreachable, causing NG setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB 的 NG-AMF 介面 IP 設定為不同的私有網路範圍而沒有路由，會使 AMF 無法到達，造成 NG 設定失敗。

explanation_en: Setting the gNB's NGU interface IP to an unreachable network range will prevent UPF connectivity, disrupting user plane traffic flow.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB 的 NGU 介面 IP 設定為無法到達的網路範圍，會阻止 UPF 連線，干擾使用者平面流量流動。

explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP will prevent the CU from connecting to the DU, causing F1 interface setup failure.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 位址設定為無法到達的 IP，會阻止 CU 連接到 DU，造成 F1 介面設定失敗。

explanation_en: An invalid IP address format for the local SCTP interface will cause binding failure during F1 setup, preventing DU connection.
explanation_zh: 本地 SCTP 介面的無效 IP 位址格式會在 F1 設定期間造成綁定失敗，阻止 DU 連線。

explanation_en: An invalid IP address format for the remote SCTP interface will cause connection failure during F1 setup, preventing DU communication.
explanation_zh: 遠端 SCTP 介面的無效 IP 位址格式會在 F1 設定期間造成連線失敗，阻止 DU 通訊。

explanation_en: An invalid IP address format for the AMF will cause NG interface initialization failure, preventing gNB registration.
explanation_zh: AMF 的無效 IP 位址格式會造成 NG 介面初始化失敗，阻止 gNB 註冊。

explanation_en: An invalid IP address format for the NG-AMF interface will cause network binding failure, preventing AMF communication.
explanation_zh: NG-AMF 介面的無效 IP 位址格式會造成網路綁定失敗，阻止 AMF 通訊。

explanation_en: An invalid IP address format for the NGU interface will cause network binding failure, preventing UPF communication.
explanation_zh: NGU 介面的無效 IP 位址格式會造成網路綁定失敗，阻止 UPF 通訊。

explanation_en: Setting the S1U port to an out-of-range value will cause socket binding failure, preventing GTP-U tunnel establishment.
explanation_zh: 將 S1U 連接埠設定為超出範圍的值會造成 socket 綁定失敗，阻止 GTP-U 隧道建立。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP control port to an out-of-range value will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1-C connection.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為超出範圍的值會造成 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1-C 連線。

explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP control port to an out-of-range value will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1-C connection.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 控制連接埠設定為超出範圍的值會造成 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1-C 連線。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP data port to an out-of-range value will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1-U connection.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 資料連接埠設定為超出範圍的值會造成 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1-U 連線。

explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP data port to an out-of-range value will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1-U connection.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 資料連接埠設定為超出範圍的值會造成 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1-U 連線。

explanation_en: Setting SCTP input streams to zero will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1 connection.
explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸入流設定為零會造成 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1 連線。

explanation_en: Setting SCTP output streams to zero will cause SCTP association failure, preventing F1 connection.
explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸出流設定為零會造成 SCTP 關聯失敗，阻止 F1 連線。

explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to a negative value will cause thread initialization failure, leading to gNB startup failure.
explanation_zh: 將 Num_Threads_PUSCH 設定為負值會造成執行緒初始化失敗，導致 gNB 啟動失敗。

explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to a value exceeding the allowed range will cause configuration validation failure, preventing gNB initialization.
explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為超出允許範圍的值會造成配置驗證失敗，阻止 gNB 初始化。

explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to a value exceeding the allowed range will cause configuration validation failure, preventing gNB initialization.
explanation_zh: 將 tracking_area_code 設定為超出允許範圍的值會造成配置驗證失敗，阻止 gNB 初始化。

explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a value exceeding the allowed range will cause configuration validation failure, preventing gNB initialization.
explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為超出允許範圍的值會造成配置驗證失敗，阻止 gNB 初始化。

explanation_en: Setting mcc to a value exceeding the allowed range will cause configuration validation failure, preventing gNB initialization.
explanation_zh: 將 mcc 設定為超出允許範圍的值會造成配置驗證失敗，阻止 gNB 初始化。

explanation_en: Setting mnc to a value exceeding the allowed range will cause configuration validation failure, preventing gNB initialization.
explanation_zh: 將 mnc 設定為超出允許範圍的值會造成配置驗證失敗，阻止 gNB 初始化。

explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to a loopback address makes the AMF unreachable, causing NG interface connection failure and preventing UE registration.
explanation_zh: 將 AMF IP 位址設定為回環位址會使 AMF 無法連線，導致 NG 介面連線失敗並阻止 UE 註冊。

explanation_en: Setting the CU's NG AMF interface IP to the same as the AMF IP causes IP address conflict and routing failure, preventing NG interface establishment and UE attachment.
explanation_zh: 將 CU 的 NG AMF 介面 IP 設定為與 AMF IP 相同會造成 IP 位址衝突和路由失敗，阻止 NG 介面建立和 UE 附接。

explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP address to the same as the remote SCTP address causes binding conflict, preventing F1 interface connection establishment with DU.
explanation_zh: 將本地 SCTP 位址設定為與遠端 SCTP 位址相同會造成綁定衝突，阻止與 DU 的 F1 介面連線建立。

explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP in a different subnet prevents F1 interface connection establishment with DU due to routing misconfiguration.
explanation_zh: 將遠端 SCTP 位址設定為不同子網路中無法連線的 IP 會因路由錯誤配置而阻止與 DU 的 F1 介面連線建立。

explanation_en: Setting the NGU interface IP to an unreachable address in a different subnet prevents GTP-U tunnel establishment and data path connectivity with UPF.
explanation_zh: 將 NGU 介面 IP 設定為不同子網路中無法連線的位址會阻止與 UPF 的 GTP-U 隧道建立和資料路徑連線。
